16
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,199
No.

17
00:02:40,439 --> 00:02:42,280
Irritable, aggressive.

18
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:46,080
Li Si said you need me.

19
00:02:46,159 --> 00:02:46,960
Do you mean...

20
00:02:49,639 --> 00:02:50,680
You pervert.

21
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,560
What am I doing?

22
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:50,120
