25
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:01,360
It's a pheromone mark.

26
00:04:02,159 --> 00:04:03,039
That means

27
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:04,120
at this stage,

28
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,520
