30
00:04:12,719 --> 00:04:14,879
So it will disappear, right?

31
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:18,399
Anyway, I will find a solution.

32
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,839
So you haven't found a solution yet?

33
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:22,639
No.

34
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:25,279
I want you to be my research object,

35
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:27,120
