36
00:04:27,639 --> 00:04:28,519
And the mark.

37
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:29,800
So offensive.

38
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,279
Anyway, let's not meet for a while.

39
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,199
Wait.

40
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,279
Sit down and talk.

41
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:46,360
You...

42
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,040
Stand up.

43
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,079
Interesting.

44
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:02,360
