57
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,040
Don't disturb the business of the merchants.

58
00:05:42,079 --> 00:05:42,720
Don't worry, My Lord.

59
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:45,120
My Lord,

60
00:05:47,759 --> 00:05:48,680
I used to be

61
