on Wuyan Island.

62
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:52,160
I've followed you for over a decade.

63
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:53,759
I'm the only one who's aged.

64
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,279
They're still young.

65
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:56,720
Out there,

66
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,000
