69
00:06:04,639 --> 00:06:06,680
How did you meet my brother?

70
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:07,800
Would you share that with me?

71
00:06:08,399 --> 00:06:09,120
Back then,

72
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:11,879
