73
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,439
Do you remember?

74
00:06:13,879 --> 00:06:14,759
That was

75
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:16,199
16 years ago.

76
00:06:18,319 --> 00:06:18,800
Wang.

77
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,000
It's late.

78
00:06:20,879 --> 00:06:21,600
Go to bed.

79
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:23,560
Okay.

80
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,839
Should I prepare a guest room for Miss Jiang?

81
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,199
No need.

82
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,000
I'll just stay here.

83
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:34,079
In case your bad allergy acts up,

84
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:34,959
