120
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,519
Kill her.

121
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,559
But if the mark comes from your oath,

122
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:50,840
unless we awaken the memory of Li Feiyuan

123
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,039
in Ms Jiang,

124
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:53,799
you'll never

125
